#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""Editorial polish pass for the Catalan generated files.

This is not a machine translator. It applies a curated glossary and recurring
phrase fixes found during review, so the generated Catalan draft becomes usable
and keeps terminology consistent across the site.
"""

